high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the sink, then turn to your right and go to the counter top across from you.
Pick up the spoon on the edge of the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink on your right.
Place the spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the kitchen counter just right of the sink
Pick up the spoon from the counter
Turn left and walk up to the kitchen sink
Put the spoon in the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: Put the spoon in the kitchen sink

high_descs: Cross the room to the left and face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the spoon up from the counter.
Go left and then turn to the right and face the sink.
Put the spoon on the counter in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon on the counter in front of the sink.
